    <item>
      <title>斯洛伐克称乌克兰不和可能导致燃料出口减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/slovakia-says-ukraine-discord-could-cause-cut-in-fuel-exports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯洛伐克表示，如果饱受战争蹂躏的国家继续实施制裁，切断俄罗斯管道原油出口，该国可能被迫削减对包括乌克兰在内的邻国的燃料出口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/slovakia-says-ukraine-discord-could-cause-cut-in-fuel-exports</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 15:39:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果英国实现住房建设目标，Starmer 将获得巨额增长奖励</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/huge-growth-prize-seen-for-starmer-if-uk-hits-housebuilding-goal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[野村证券 (Nomura) 经济学家表示，如果首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 在本届议会任期内成功建造 150 万套新房，英国的经济增长率将获得大幅提升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/huge-growth-prize-seen-for-starmer-if-uk-hits-housebuilding-goal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 15:39:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对“无受害人”案件中 4.54 亿美元欺诈判决提出质疑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/trump-challenges-454-million-fraud-verdict-in-victimless-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普请求曼哈顿上诉法院推翻针对他的 4.54 亿美元民事欺诈判决，称该案没有受害者，且裁决赋予纽约总检察长“无限权力”追捕政治对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/trump-challenges-454-million-fraud-verdict-in-victimless-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 15:26:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>博茨瓦纳向公民承诺将持有新矿业公司 24% 的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/botswana-touts-24-stake-in-new-mining-companies-for-citizens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[博茨瓦纳政府将鼓励新的矿业企业向公民提供购买高达 24％ 的国有股权的权利，而这些国有股权尚未被国家行使购买权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/botswana-touts-24-stake-in-new-mining-companies-for-citizens</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 15:23:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
